        "## Exercise 5: Portfolio Backtest\n",
        "\n",
        "We evaluate four strategies over portfolio-return months **January 2010 – December 2024** (portfolios formed December 2009 – November 2024). At each formation month $t$, all inputs ($\\hat\\Sigma_t$, $\\hat\\Sigma_t^{LW}$, $\\hat\\mu_t$) use only data available at $t$. We set $\\gamma=4$ and $\\lambda=0.1$.\n",
        "\n",
        "Net excess returns deduct the quadratic transaction cost implied by the optimisation objective:\n",
        "$$r_t^{\\mathrm{net}} = \\omega_t'\\,r_{t+1} - \\lambda(\\omega_t - \\omega_t^{+})'\\hat\\Sigma_t(\\omega_t - \\omega_t^{+}).$$\n",
        "Monthly turnover follows @hautsch2019 equation 46: $\\mathrm{TO}_t = \\sum_i|\\omega_{i,t} - \\omega_{i,t}^{+}|$."
      ],
